Package: org.grails.datastore.gorm.cassandra

[Java] Class InList

        • org.grails.datastore.gorm.cassandra.InList

        • Override convertArguments implementation to prevent conversion if conversionService cannot convert, just like the MethodExpression implementation. Prevents conversion of composite primary key maps and other types such as Enum, URL etc. which will be converted in CassandraQuery using CassandraEntityPersister
